node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mother of Draguns on August 26, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, child and flower.

node.text: God, thank u. u have given me many roles in this life and none i take more seriously than God Father. my beautiful niece Eva is my everything and grounds me to not being as reckless knowing i have a responsibility to her forever... and yes i said God Father. i told my family that god mother makes me sound like an old fairy lady... but God Father makes me sounds like a boss. this is gonna be a fun one for Baby Eva to have to explain one day... i know it might be confusing to y’all and u might not get it. but u don’t have to. this is for me and my family. i’m Tia Nina and God Father Dragun.

node.text: u can look don’t touch this 🔥 every day is a fight. a fight to continue. a fight to be urself. a fight just to just get out of bed in the morning. this is my art piece and outlet of expressing myself. i’m enjoying learning my body and how to use it to speak on my emotions... y’all i’m sensitive with all this i know i’m not the best but u know i’ll always GIVE everything i have and then some. discovering my body thru dance has been such a new exciting experience. i was born a fighter. creative director @mikeyminden chero @monicagiavanna filmed @robfish_inc

node.text: all the rumors are true. fake azz. fake boobz. yeah... idk how to explain it but i’m happier than i’ve been in a long time. there’s no rule book on how to live this lifestyle and it’s definitely NOT for everyone. in my life i’ve had to dim my own shine in order to make those around me more comfortable... BYE. i can feel myself growing and maturing into an even stronger woman. i stopped being myself online awhile ago in order to protect my sanity really... trying to please everyone ain’t cutting it. u either F with me or u don’t babezzz... but i’m open and ready to share again. ready to laugh. love. make some mistakes and GROW. cus that’s what humans do. consider this a chapter turned in the book of dragun ♥️
